<li><b><i>Partition Boot Record (PBR):</i></b>
Partition Boot Record w skrócie PBR, nazywany tak¿e 
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=biosboot&amp;sektion=8&amp;arch=i386">biosboot(8)</a>
